          ? &#39;sm-location&#39;
          : location &gt; 10
            ? &#39;lg-location&#39;
            : &#39;md-location&#39;
      }
    }

... which will produce `sm-location` class if location value is under `5`, `lg-location` if above `10` or `md-location` otherwise. Obviously, change the mapper to whatever makes sense for your case.

